151
00:08:38,898 --> 00:08:42,435
of nature, not a technological limitation. It's built into the

152
00:08:42,535 --> 00:08:47,009
mathematical structure of quantum mechanics through the commutation relations.

153
00:08:48,109 --> 00:08:50,384
We've journeyed through one of quantum mechanics'

